-- UBS March Consumption Indicator Rises to Highest in Eight Months
-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 2012-04-27T06:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-27/ubs-march-consumption-indicator-rises-to-highest-in-eight-months.html
A gauge of Swiss consumer demand
rose to the highest in eight months in March,  UBS AG (UBSN)  said.  The consumption indicator, which signals developments about
three months ahead, advanced to 1.22 points from a revised 0.9
points in February, the Zurich-based bank said in an e-mailed
statement today. It had previously reported a February
reading of 0.87 points.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paul Verschuur in Zurich at 
